data.name: YTV2 YouTube Views [AdWords] (Engagement) (1k/10M)  (Lifetime Guarantee)
data.description:
100% legit and safe views from regular YouTube users - not bots nor paid to watch free lancers. We do not cheat Google with credit accounts, so your channels have no risk of getting shadow ban (in which case it becomes difficult to promote them even with legit AdWords accounts). Start time is 12 to 72 hours. Non drop.

Contrary to the cheaper version, where views come from in-stream preroll ads (with users having no way to interact with your video), these views come from the in-feed (former discovery) ads, when users have to click on banner ad and transfer to your video's page, where they can interact with your video as usually - that's is like, share, comment and subscribe. So, if your video will be interesting to average Joe, you will normally get 5 to 15 real subs for every thousand of such views you order, who may watch and share other videos of yours as well and thus help your channel grow faster (especially if you post a few new vids of the same niche each week and watch the quality of their picture and sound).

No live stream, premier, drugs, guns, gamble, casino, violence, shocking, political nor COVID-19 related videos are accepted (further restrictions may be applied by Google). Video duration can be anywhere from 11 seconds to 18 hours, but prefer videos up to 5 minutes long - the shorter your video the faster it will receive views and vice versa. Duration recommended for paid promotion on YouTube by Google itself is up to 3 minutes.

To use this service your video must be in one of the languages supported by Google AdWords: Arabic, Bengali, Bulgarian, Catalan, Chinese, Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch, English, Estonian, Filipino, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Hindi, Hungarian, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Latvian, Lithuanian, Malay, Malayalam, Marathi, Norwegian, Polish, Portuguese, Romanian, Russian, Serbian, Slovak, Slovenian, Spanish, Swedish, Tamil, Telugu, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Urdu, Vietnamese.

Monetization allowed. Note, that most of the views may be delivered in the last few days, stats at your dashboard may be renewed after the order completion (but you can track them right from the start in your YouTube Analytics under the YouTube advertising source) and around 20% of orders get rejected by YouTube or do not receive any views (in which case the funds for undelivered views will be refunded to your balance at our panel, so you could try with another video or the worldwide version of views, if it wasn't used before).

If your order was canceled, please, do not reorder with the same link and service, cause your order will be canceled again, since once a video is rejected by YT ads platform and has not passed the appellation successfully or has received little to no views at all, there is no point in reordering it, and it's a good free indicator that your video is not favored by the YouTube algorithms and you should try with another one (or reducing it to 3-10 minutes for worldwide and 3-5 minutes for GEO targeted versions - duration favored by the YouTube ads service).
